through this whole long process to kind of

00:04:13.799 --> 00:04:18.370
find the moments in the book. And the good
news is that as I was pulling up in my car

00:04:18.370 --> 00:04:22.001
that I just found out from my editor from
Harper Collins that it made the New York Times

00:04:22.001 --> 00:04:28.440
best seller list so I am really excited. Yeah.
[applause]

