If they took my money, I would have felt better

00:05:38.111 --> 00:05:43.150
about it. It would be a goal-oriented behavior.
Instead it was just violence for the fuck

00:05:43.150 --> 00:05:44.420
of it.

00:05:44.420 --> 00:05:49.020
