What was amazing when I did these interviews

00:11:47.249 --> 00:11:50.249
and I interviewed people like Chuck Berry
who invented Rock and Roll basically, and

00:11:50.249 --> 00:11:56.879
Bo Diddly who and Jerry Lewis who left like
such a huge legacy on music. And it here's

00:11:56.879 --> 00:12:00.880
these guys, who like are almost afraid to
go outside, who think everybody hates them

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:06.160
because of some scandal that happened like
thirty years ago. The lesson from that is

00:12:06.160 --> 00:12:10.250
that literally, we've all have shitty things
happen to us in the past. We all have, you

00:12:10.250 --> 00:12:15.671
know, whatever whether it's relationship or
a parenting thing or a scandal or a, you know,

00:12:15.671 --> 00:12:19.210
some humiliation something that didn't work
out. You deal with it the best you can at

00:12:19.210 --> 00:12:24.410
the moment. Then you have to let go and move
on. And the crazy thing is that all the shitty

00:12:24.410 --> 00:12:29.410
things, in the moment, like enrich you later.
Not just as a person, but actually to other

00:12:29.410 --> 00:12:32.559
people. And you'll see in the book, like I
was trying to explain to Chuck Berry, that

00:12:32.559 --> 00:12:37.240
yeah, maybe when you transported a minor across
state lines for immoral purposes, that was

00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:41.529
bad at the time and you went to jail. That's
true. And at the time, it really did hurt

00:12:41.529 --> 00:12:46.050
and destroy your career. The crazy ironic
thing is that although that may that is still

00:12:46.050 --> 00:12:50.339
wrong, it actually just made you more interesting
to people now. No one's judging you for it

00:12:50.339 --> 00:12:56.180
anymore; it's just a story now. And I think
if like that's true for that, a lot of what

00:12:56.180 --> 00:12:59.990
we've been through, it becomes that too.
So letting go of the past, and focusing on

00:12:59.990 --> 00:13:06.010
what, you know, focusing on being great at
what you enjoy and be glad of your accomplishments

00:13:06.010 --> 00:13:11.889
is important.
