and especially in LA, like trying to feel,

00:13:22.480 --> 00:13:26.610
like feeling like, if they get famous or get
a lot of money, that's going to fix all their

00:13:26.610 --> 00:13:32.569
problems of insignificance; of insecurity;
of worthlessness and disconnection. And of

00:13:32.569 --> 00:13:38.660
course, the real lesson is that rather than
fixing one's problems like the more fame and

00:13:38.660 --> 00:13:42.339
wealth like magnify them. And those little
things that aren't a big problem in your life

00:13:42.339 --> 00:13:47.249
become huge and that's where we get to enjoy
on the front page of the tabloids and watching

00:13:47.249 --> 00:13:53.830
Charlie Sheen, and then everything else.
And the corollary to that then is that fix

00:13:53.830 --> 00:13:58.189
your problems now because the older you get,
